查看庆祝“The Mighty Boosh”20 周年新展览的独家照片https://www.nme.com/news/tv/mighty-boosh-20th-anniversary-exhibition-exclusive-photos-dave-brown-3801066?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=mighty-boosh-20th-anniversary-exhibition-独家照片-戴夫·布朗Andrew TrendellWed, 09 Oct 2024 12:40:00 +0000 Music NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3801066 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“Boosh 20 背后”。图片来源：戴夫·布朗" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>通过 Behind The Boosh 20 获得幕后巅峰</p><p>《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/tv/mighty-boosh-20th-anniversary-exhibition-exclusive-photos-dave-brown-3801066">查看庆祝“The Mighty Boosh”20 周年新展览的独家照片》</a>一文首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="“Boosh 20 背后”。图片来源：戴夫·布朗" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Nannas_19_-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>为了庆祝纪念<em><a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-mighty-boosh">The Mighty Boosh</a></em> 20 周年的新展览开幕，请查看下面由 Dave Brown 在<em>NME</em>上拍摄的独家照片。</p><p> <em>Behind The Boosh 20</em>去年夏天首次在澳大利亚展出，并将于 10 月 10 日至 13 日在位于霍克斯顿街 2 号的 Behind The Gallery 展出，为这部关于失败音乐家变成动物园的开创性且捕捉时代精神的超现实喜剧幕后提供了一个高峰。霍华德·穆恩 (Howard Moon) 和文斯·诺尔 (Vince Noir) 是饲养员和后来的店主。</p><p>这些照片是由演员戴夫·布朗拍摄的，他在剧中扮演猿猴博洛，他捕捉到了喜剧团在后台和圣路易斯的坦率时刻。</p><p>布朗在一份新闻稿中表示：“我完全否认，自从 2004 年我在第一季第一集《Killeroo》中扮演 Joey Moose 以来，已经过去 20 年了。” 。 “当时我有一部诺基亚砖头手机，社交媒体只有 Friends Reunited 和 MySpace， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/FRANZ-FERDINAND">Franz Ferdinand</a>排名第一，Rich Fulcher 烫发。”</p><p>他补充道：“我已经有一段时间没有向英国粉丝展示<em>《Behind The Boosh》的</em>照片了！能让我的猴子手回到布满灰尘的 Boosh 档案中，找到一些粉丝最喜欢的经典老歌，真是太棒了，但我也热衷于展示所有电视和现场表演中从未见过的时刻。”</p><p>下面查看朱利安·巴拉特 (Julian Barratt)、诺埃尔·菲尔丁 (Noel Fielding)、里奇·福尔彻 (Rich Fulcher) 等人的精选独家照片，以及布朗对他捕捉到的瞬间的见解。</p><h2><strong>托尼的约会</strong></h2><figure id="attachment_3801077" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3801077" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="wp-image-3801077 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_.jpg" alt="“Boosh 20 背后”。图片来源：戴夫·布朗" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/boosh_Tonys_Appointment_19x13_-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id