www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Sabrina-Carpenter-onstage-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>许多<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/roblox"><em>《Roblox Dress To Impress</em></a> 》粉丝从<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>和她的“Short N&#39; Sweet”巡演中汲取灵感。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) – “Short n&#39; Sweet”评论：一位新的流行公主的崛起</a></strong></li></ul><p><em>Dress To Impress</em>是一款<em>Roblox</em>游戏，挑战玩家在将标志性造型展示在 T 台上之前将其组合在一起。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/roblox-users-can-finally-have-a-brat-summer-with-record-breaking-update-3784891">今年早些时候，</a>为了庆祝“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">Brat”</a>夏季，推出了受<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>启发的特别更新，但流行乐迷现在正在将事情掌握在自己手中。</p><p>萨布丽娜·卡彭特 (Sabrina Carpenter) 上个月为新专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sabrina-carpenter-short-n-sweet-review-3787293">Short N&#39; Sweet</a> 》 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sabrina-carptenter-scraps-custom-nonsense-outros-but-promises-surprise-cover-each-night-starting-with-abba-as-she-kicks-off-world-tour-3796700">开启了她规模宏大、雄心勃勃的舞台巡演</a>，演出以独特的封面、令人印象深刻的制作和大量的亮片为特色。一位粉丝在社交媒体上<a href="https://x.com/stunninbrina/status/1842199608337863004" target="_blank" rel="noopener">写道</a>：“我在秀场上的<em>着装令人印象深刻</em>”，旁边还有卡彭特在舞台上的照片。</p><p>其他人在回复这条病毒式推文时分享了他们的木匠风格<em>Dress To Impress</em>造型。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">字面上是我<a href="https://t.co/XDBNz1h4Kd">pic.twitter.com/XDBNz1h4Kd<