皮尔斯·摩根在播出捷豹赖特称 Jay-Z 和碧昂斯为“怪物”的指控后道歉https://www.nme.com/news/music/piers-morgan-apologises-airing-jaguar-wright-allegations-jay-z-beyonce-monsters-3800989?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=piers-morgan-apologises-正在播出捷豹赖特指控杰伊 Z 碧昂丝怪物Liberty DunworthWed, 09 Oct 2024 10:41:59 +0000 Music NewsNews..R&B https://www.nme.com/?p=3800989 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="皮尔斯·摩根、Jay-Z 和碧昂丝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “我们的律师联系我们说这些说法完全错误”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/piers-morgan-apologises-airing-jaguar-wright-allegations-jay-z-beyonce-monsters-3800989">皮尔斯·摩根 (Piers Morgan) 在播出捷豹·赖特 (Jaguar Wright) 指控 Jay-Z 和碧昂斯 (Beyoncé) 的指控后道歉，称 Jay-Z 和碧昂斯为“怪物”，</a>该帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="皮尔斯·摩根、Jay-Z 和碧昂丝" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan-Jay-z-Beyonce@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>皮尔斯·摩根 (Piers Morgan) 在接受采访时提出有关<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jay-z">Jay-Z</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂丝的</a>指控后发表了道歉。</p><p>这一刻发生在本周早些时候，当时歌手捷豹·赖特 (Jaguar Wright) 出现在摩根的<em>未经审查</em>节目中，并谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-arrested-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3794341">肖恩·“迪迪”·库姆斯 (Sean &#39;Diddy&#39; Combs) 最近被捕的</a>情况。</p><p>在这场病毒式传播的讨论中，赖特还利用该平台对 Jay-Z 和碧昂丝提出了指控，声称他们两人都有“数百名受害者”。</p><p> “四年来，我尖叫的不仅仅是 Diddy，还有 Diddy 和 Jay-Z 都是怪物，”她补充道。</p><p>现在，摩根向观众解释说，Jay-Z 和碧昂丝的律师已经联系了他，并为播放他的客人的言论而道歉。</p><p> “关于平台，现代世界的现实是，几乎每个人都有一个平台，只要他们有话要说，其他人想听，”摩根在昨天的节目（10 月 8 日）中说道。 “这就是我们邀请[赖特]接受采访的原因。提出这些主张的人无论有没有像我这样的节目都有观众。” </p><figure id="attachment_3800997" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3800997" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3800997" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270.jpg" alt="皮尔斯·摩根" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Piers-Morgan@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3800997" class="wp-caption-text">皮尔斯·摩根.图片来源：JORAS/GC Images/Getty</figcaption></figure><p>他继续说道，“嗯，出乎意料的是，捷豹在那次采访中对 Jay-Z 和碧昂丝提出了几项严重指控。正如我当时所说，他们并没有在场回应或为自己辩护，但现在他们做到了。我们有律师联系我们，说这些说法完全错误，没有事实依据，因此我们遵守了法律要求，将它们从最初的采访中删除。”</p><p>最后，他说：“在一场名为<em>“未经审查”</em>的节目中，编辑采访并不是我们轻易做的事情，但就像众所周知的拥挤剧院中的火灾呼喊一样，我们也受到法律限制。我们向 Jay-Z 和碧昂斯道歉。”</p><p>迪迪（本名肖恩·库姆斯）上个月<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-arrested-sexual-misconduct-allegations-3794341">在纽约被捕</a>，并被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-charged-with-sex-trafficking-racketeering-and-transporting-for-prostitution-3794598">指控犯有性交易、敲诈勒索和运送卖淫</a><i>的</i>罪名。他对所有指控均表示不认罪。</p><p>他被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/diddy-denied-bail-in-sex-trafficking-racketeering-case-3794666">拒绝保释</a>，据报道<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/p-diddy-reportedly-placed-on-suicide-watch-while-awaiting-trial-for-sex-crimes-3795772">在等待审判期间受到自杀监视</a>，一些报道表明<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/paranoid-diddy-reportedly-not-eating-prison-fear-poisoned-3796772">他因担心中毒而没有在监狱里吃饭</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3794343" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3794343" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="wp-image-3794343 size-full" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270.jpg" alt="吹牛老爹 (Diddy) 在 2023 年 MTV VMA 颁奖典礼上" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/diddy@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-att